description "Lando Calrissian

Class: Hero
Brief Overview: 
A fast melee/gunner hybrid that moves in and out of combat with ease, and can disguise himself. 

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Vibro-Axe
-- Based on Lightsaber
-- Yellow/Red styles
-- Saber Defense (1)
-- Cannot block blasters
- S-5 Heavy Pistol 
-- Based on WESTAR-34 Pistol (2)
-- 10% higher FP damage
-- 20% faster reload speed
- E-11 Blaster Rifle (3)
-- Based on EE-4
- Stun/Frag Grenades (3)
-- Alt. fire detonates on contact

^8Attributes:
- Healing (2)
- Shield Recharge (1)

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (2) [Class Special 1]
- Dash (2) [Class Special 2]
- Quickthrow (2) [Class Special 3 outside grenades]
- Spy Disguise (1) [Alt. mode in melee]

Lando Calrissian has a dark past but has recently stumbled into good fortune as a mining colony administrator, that is until the Empire came to Cloud City. Now holding a position of Commander in the Rebellion Lando works to free the galaxy from the tyranny of the Emperor."